S.|title=The official Gun Digest book of guns & prices 2012|date=2012|publisher=Krause Publications|location=Iola, WI|isbn=1440229279|page=32|edition=7th|url=https://books.google.com/books?id=me1tha-egPkC&lpg=PA32&dq=ASAI%20One%20Pro%2045&pg=PA32#v=onepage&q=ASAI%20One%20Pro%2045&f=false|accessdate=27 September 2014}}) [[Switzerland]].{{cite book|last1=Fjestad|first1=S.P.|title=Blue Book of Gun Values|date=1997|publisher=Blue Book Publications|location=Minneapolis, MN|isbn=1-886768-08-0|page=102|edition=18th}} It was at one time imported into the USA by Magnum Research and into Italy by ALGIMEC. == References == {{reflist}} == External links == * [http://www.asai-ag.ch/onepro45.html Company webpage] * [http://www.securityarms.com/20010315/galleryfiles/1600/1624.htm Security Arms website] - Picture * [https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=PB-XFQKQPus ASAI OnePro Review] - Video [[Category:.45 ACP firearms]] [[Category:Semi-automatic pistols of Switzerland]]
